    <abstract id="aspace_14f03aa40112c7582e856e65ade1d4a2">The Curt Royston Papers consists of reviews, promotional matierals, transparencies, film, and video recordings relating to Royston's career as a filmmaker. Materials date from 1982 to 2000.</abstract>
    <physloc id="aspace_013d4cc9afea5ee556d16d5b763eb8b8">Some materials are stored offsite and advance notice is required for use. Please contact fales.library@nyu.edu at least two business days prior to your research visit to coordinate access.</physloc>
    <langmaterial id="aspace_9a9e560fca9d7dfca34c80d1e5de9148">Materials are in English.</langmaterial>
