  <acqinfo id="aspace_33ba4c0d40047f97b9379bbcb91292aa">
    <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
<p>Donated by Curt Royston in 2009 and 2014. The accession numbers associated with these gifts are 2009.259 and 2014.259.</p>  </acqinfo>
