    </list>
  </arrangement>
  <bioghist id="aspace_d896d7d9e55fbfa0e3e0383d84855c69">
    <head>Biographical Note</head>
<p>Curt Royston is best known for his proficiency in a variety of media: painting, sculpture, photography, film, and video, and often in combination. His work has been shown extensively throughout the United States and Europe including a 1987 one-man exhibition at the Whitney Museum of American Art.</p>  </bioghist>
