  <scopecontent id="aspace_a9e3b41c3052b60c233031a83580c3a9">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>This collection contains reviews, promotional matierals, transparencies, film, and video recordings relating to Curt Royston's career as a filmmaker. Materials date from 1982 to 2000.</p>  </scopecontent>
